tml\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hdt1665702766826.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hdt1665702766826.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hdt1665702766826\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      putmess\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__putmess_66464\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the destination of the message frame output. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__topic_d19496e1_d19497e1_d19498e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__p_d19499e1_d19500e1_d19501e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">PUTmess</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__topic_d14042e1_d14043e1_d14044e1_d14045e1_d14046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d523520e68\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__li_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—send message frame output to the\n               message frame. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hdt1665702766826__li_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—redirect message frame output to the screen. Messages that are normally sent to the message frame appear immediately on the screen. Use ^REFRESH to repaint the screen and remove these messages.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/whw1665702766757.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>dump</a><p>Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528167\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528167\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "putmess Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 putmess Specify the destination of the message frame output. PUTmess off | on Arguments on —send message frame output to the message frame. off —redirect message frame output to the screen. Messages that are normally sent to the message frame appear immediately on the screen. Use ^REFRESH to repaint the screen and remove these messages. Related Links dump Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}